Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take point up ahead.\NStay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel afterward?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think my memory is breaking off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Should anything goes wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing feels scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be a drug developed\Nby the OSF hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They just left it in an underground tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be some kind of drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless there is a severe episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's best not to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Some OSF soldiers who defected to\Nthe Seiran Garrison
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,were spotted in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What were doing in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DUBIOUS AMPOULE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the report
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,actually be misinformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look around for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only mission we can carry out\Nfor the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. Before we could determine\Nwhat's the next step to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking action to correct\NNew Himuka government's misconduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point in our career, Karen and I\Nbecame comrades who shared the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was investigating the cause\Nof my late fiancee’s metamorphosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered their rehabilitation program\Nand metamorphosis experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to change this nation from within,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,given we were in the inner circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Karen wasn't the man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,our superior would approve of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I accepted the orders from our superior
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to reshuffle our ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Karen is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no point for me to keep playing\Nthe government's lapdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will change this twisted nation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with an approach that is different from Karen's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A different approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The government conducted\Nillegal human experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our people must know about their misconduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The government has been keeping\Nthe people in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt disclosing this secret to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,could make up for all the horrible things\Nthey have done in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least it should mark\Nthe beginning of change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Karen works on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,while Major General Fubuki\Nworks from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to change this country\Nby working on both ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's our intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way I can help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a word with my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best not to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Chief Sumeragi is your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But he is also an official.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't like what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi and Nagi were...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me help, Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you are their captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When it concerns the country's\Nclassified information,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,your team will also face punishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand its magnitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll stop being their captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the only way to work this out\Nis for us to share your ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel pity for Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is all the government's doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I could give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, since you insist on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am in charge of the planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, carry out the missions\Nyou are given.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The new safety measures for Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford another Suoh incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, I plan to enter Arahabaki's secure site.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll inform the control center\Nto let you access it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here! Above us, at 12 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters, we're not here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brain wave is not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop using your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping, thank you, out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, am, I.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Happened, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, my head is splitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kunad Gate is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like a reaction to its exterior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Naomi replied to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't use my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The anomaly is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All stats are normal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fine after I took the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If the pain wasn't gone,\NI wouldn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So can we assume the drug is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a weird stench. It tasted awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, there is something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, do you detect anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The extinction belt above is too thick,\NI can't capture the reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I need more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two of them.\NThey are heading to Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the image now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These are trucks from Seiran Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they came from Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it was a city founded by people\Nwho worship the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They became a tiny autonomous country\Nafter their independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Kagero's hometown was Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the target we've been looking for has shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those the trucks we saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get any information on the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is fairly remote.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be a Seiran facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives me the creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Luka found something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what those trucks were transporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There are similar items on the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wasn't mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of production line?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same item transported by the trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all human brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they processing human brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is their motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This stench feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The stench? It does stink in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Spring Pharmaceuticals making these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, put yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and his team are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems to be the case. Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and the others found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If the secret of this facility is known\Nto the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to protect my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tsugumi.\NThings became pretty ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place, Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you already know the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Spring Pharmaceuticals' Seiran factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,More precisely speaking, they are running it\Nwith the Seiran government.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an Other research center.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, do you know what kind of research\Nthey are conducting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the ampoule you shot Naomi with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Human brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say "brains?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you inject my sister with that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This research center's goal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is to defeat New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They are researching on Other weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Other weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan back then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was to transplant human brains onto Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we connected the brain\Nof a user with SAS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But the plan changed. They decided to use\Nsuitable candidates by turning them into Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The process requires
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the ampoule to sedate the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're planning to use\Nmy sister as weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was only an excuse\Nfor my operation in Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The actual goal of this facility
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is to turn Other back to their human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you allow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for the sake of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you helping them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really was you who killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane is trying to kill Yuito for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just New Himuka,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,even Seiran is full of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They are using human brains to make drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But without the ampoule,\NI can't save my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This discovery is indeed terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But this drug is without a doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,needed by some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I must protect my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back, Luka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, why did you let them go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the people find out about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, don't you have any objection\Nregarding the ampoule's ingredient?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane isn't ready to make the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We are just the same as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't sure if we're really killing Yuito
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether we are siding with Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know the drug was\Nmade with human brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the researchers' conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and the others saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Had I known it was human brains,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that thing in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ampoule
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,gives you the ability to talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are human brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that make me just as terrible as Other?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I must tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll find a way to make your human again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't give up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave me alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We should wait for Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he ask us to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell us the next plan of action?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That ampoule factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki is connected\Nto Spring Pharmaceuticals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he already knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru told me what happened in Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a report to the government
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,with information that won't hinder our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring Pharmaceuticals belongs to your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the more reason for me\Nto report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Exposing my family's dirty little secret
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will earn me the government's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who suggested for Seiran\Nto build that facility
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,were Karen and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,THE TRAITOR YUITO
